INSTALLATION FROM SOURCE TARBALL

1. Get the current source tarball from http://spambri.de/quadkonsole4
	curl -O http://spambri.de/quadkonsole4/quadkonsole4-<version>.tar.xz
2. Unpack it and change into the unpacked directory
	tar -xaf quadkonsole4-<version>.tar.xz
	cd quadkonsole4
3. Create a build directory to separate source from temporary files
	mkdir build
	cd build
4. Configure and compile
	cmake ..
	make
5. Install (requires root privileges)
	make install
